msgctxt "12625"
msgid ""
"おい、見たか。\n"
"俺がお前を筆頭にすると言った時の連中の反応。"
msgstr "Hey, did you see it? Their reaction when I said you were the first."

msgctxt "12686"
msgid ""
"最近は勤王党も、妙に堅苦しい組織に\n"
"なってきちまってたからな。\n"
"良い起爆剤になったろうぜ。"
msgstr ""
"Recently, the Qin Wang Party has become a strangely rigid organization. It "
"would have been a good detonator."

msgctxt "12777"
msgid ""
"古参の連中からは、\n"
"あまり良く思われないだろうな。"
msgstr "It doesn't look very good to the old guys."

msgctxt "12828"
msgid ""
"いいんだよ、それくらいで。\n"
"あれ位の刺激がねぇと、下の連中も焦らない。\n"
"組織ってのは、固まっちまったら終いだ。"
msgstr ""
"That's fine. Without that kind of stimulation, the people below wouldn't be "
"impatient either. The organization is over when it's solidified."

msgctxt "12939"
msgid "土佐藩がいい例だろ？"
msgstr "The Tosa domain is a good example, isn't it?"

msgctxt "12960"
msgid "まあ、そうだが……"
msgstr "Well, that's right ..."

msgctxt "12980"
msgid "……まだ痛むのか？　背中。"
msgstr "...... Does it still hurt? back."

msgctxt "13007"
msgid ""
"ん？　おお、これか？\n"
"いや、痛みはねぇさ。\n"
"まぁ跡だけは派手に残っちまってるがな。"
msgstr ""
"Hmm? Oh, is this? No, it doesn't hurt. Well, only the traces are left "
"flashy."

msgctxt "13090"
msgid "すまねえ、兄弟。"
msgstr "I'm sorry, brothers."

msgctxt "13107"
msgid ""
"もう謝んなって言ったろ？\n"
"いつの話だ。"
msgstr "Did you say apologize? When is the story?"

msgctxt "13146"
msgid ""
"１５年前だ。\n"
"だが今でも昨日のことのように思い出す。"
msgstr "15 years ago. But I still remember it like yesterday."

msgctxt "13199"
msgid "まあ、忘れようったって忘れられねえか……"
msgstr "Well, can't you forget that you've forgotten ..."

msgctxt "13240"
msgid ""
"上士による焼き討ち。\n"
"目の前で両親と家が焼け落ちるのを\n"
"見ちまってんだからな。"
msgstr ""
"Burning down by a superior. I was watching my parents and my house burn down"
" in front of me."

msgctxt "13319"
msgid ""
"あの時、兄弟が助けてくれなかったら、\n"
"俺ぁ両親共々、灰にされてた。"
msgstr ""
"At that time, if my brothers didn't help me, my parents would have been "
"ashes."

msgctxt "13386"
msgid ""
"だが俺を助けたせいで、兄弟は大火傷を……\n"
"本当にすまないと思ってる。"
msgstr ""
"But because of my help, my brother got a big burn ... I'm really sorry."

msgctxt "13455"
msgid ""
"だから謝んなっつってんだろ？\n"
"謝るのはお前じゃねえ。"
msgstr "So why don't you apologize? You're not the one to apologize."

msgctxt "13508"
msgid ""
"あの日、お前の家と家族を焼いた上士どもだ。\n"
"……だろ？"
msgstr ""
"The bosses who burned your house and family that day. ...... Isn't it?"

msgctxt "13563"
msgid "……ああ。"
msgstr "……Oh."

msgctxt "13574"
msgid ""
"龍馬……\n"
"俺と親っさんは土佐藩を変えるつもりだ。\n"
"当然お前にも力になってもらいたい。"
msgstr ""
"Ryoma ... I and my parents are going to change the Tosa domain. Of course I "
"want you to help me too."

msgctxt "13659"
msgid ""
"粗方の話は聞いてる。\n"
"だが実際んとこ、何をする気なんだ？"
msgstr ""
"I'm listening to the rough story. But what are you really going to do?"

msgctxt "13716"
msgid ""
"土佐藩の天守……「高知城」を襲撃するのさ。\n"
"土佐勤王党の党員、５００人でな。"
msgstr ""
"The castle tower of the Tosa domain ... Attacking \"Kochi Castle\". There "
"are 500 members of the Tosa Qin Wang Party."

msgctxt "13793"
msgid "襲撃だと……!?"
msgstr "If it's an attack ...!?"

msgctxt "13808"
msgid ""
"襲撃っつっても、\n"
"実際には手を出さずに終わるはずだ。"
msgstr "Even if you attack, it should end without actually touching it."

msgctxt "13861"
msgid ""
"城を包囲して「勤王党の覚悟」が\n"
"藩の上層部に伝わればいい。"
msgstr ""
"Surrounding the castle, the \"preparation of the Qin Wang Party\" should be "
"conveyed to the upper ranks of the clan."

msgctxt "13920"
msgid ""
"そのうえで親っさんが城を牛耳る老人たちに\n"
"隠居を迫るんだよ。"
msgstr ""
"On top of that, parents urge the old men who dominate the castle to retire."

msgctxt "13981"
msgid ""
"万が一、老人たちがそれを拒めば……\n"
"当然、その場合の軍備はできている。"
msgstr ""
"Should the old people refuse to do so ... Of course, the armaments in that "
"case are in place."

msgctxt "14052"
msgid "そうやって空いた席に「勤王党」が座るのか？"
msgstr "Will the \"Qin Wang Party\" sit in the vacant seats like that?"

msgctxt "14095"
msgid ""
"ああ……　すぐそこに迫る危機。\n"
"命の危険を感じて初めて、上士連中は\n"
"自分たちの考えの浅はかさに気づく。"
msgstr ""
"Ah ... the crisis is just around the corner. Only when they feel the danger "
"of life, the superiors realize the shallowness of their thoughts."

msgctxt "14198"
msgid ""
"ガチガチに固まっちまった\n"
"土佐藩の身分制度を壊すには、\n"
"そのくらいの荒療治が必要だってことだ。"
msgstr ""
"It means that such rough treatment is required to break the social division "
"of the Tosa domain, which has become entrenched."

msgctxt "14293"
msgid "なるほどな……"
msgstr "got it……"

msgctxt "14308"
msgid ""
"黒船が初めてこの国に来た時と同じさ。\n"
"……脅威というものを感じることで、\n"
"人間は動揺する。"
msgstr ""
"It's the same as when Kurofune first came to this country. ...... Human "
"beings are upset by feeling a threat."

msgctxt "14399"
msgid ""
"変わらなければならないと考えるようになる。\n"
"そういうことだ。"
msgstr "I come to think that I have to change. That's how it is."

msgctxt "14460"
msgid ""
"東洋の親っさんは、\n"
"牽牛子塾を開いているときから\n"
"このことを考えてたのか？"
msgstr ""
"Did the oriental parents think about this from the time they opened the "
"Kengoshizuka Juku?"

msgctxt "14535"
msgid ""
"多分な。\n"
"……あの人は、お前に剣を、\n"
"俺には政治と学問を叩きこんだ。"
msgstr ""
"Maybe. ... that person struck you with a sword and me with politics and "
"scholarship."

msgctxt "14604"
msgid "それもすべてはこの計画のためだ。"
msgstr "It's all because of this plan."

msgctxt "14637"
msgid ""
"そうだったのか……\n"
"だが、もう剣が役立つこともなさそうだな。"
msgstr "Was that so ... but I don't think the sword will be useful anymore."

msgctxt "14698"
msgid "ん？　どうしてだ？"
msgstr "Hmm? Why?"

msgctxt "14717"
msgid ""
"きっと剣で人を斬るという時代は終わるんだろう。\n"
"実際、さっきお前もピストルの練習を\n"
"させていただろう？"
msgstr ""
"I'm sure the era of slashing people with a sword will end. In fact, did you "
"also practice pistol a while ago?"

msgctxt "14820"
msgid ""
"いやそれは、勤王党の連中には剣の才がないからだ。\n"
"剣はいくら教えても才能が無ければうまくならない。"
msgstr ""
"No, that's because the Qin Wang party doesn't have the talent for a sword. "
"No matter how much you teach a sword, you can't get better without talent."

msgctxt "14919"
msgid ""
"だがピストルは違う。\n"
"練習さえすれば、戦力になり得る。\n"
"万人に平等な武器というわけだ。"
msgstr ""
"But the pistol is different. If you practice, you can become a force. It's a"
" weapon equal to everyone."

msgctxt "15006"
msgid "平等な武器か……"
msgstr "Is it an equal weapon ..."

msgctxt "15023"
msgid ""
"龍馬……\n"
"俺らは身分という壁を壊そうとしてる。"
msgstr "Ryoma ... We are trying to break the wall of status."

msgctxt "15070"
msgid ""
"だがたとえそれが実現したとしても、\n"
"人間は決して平等になんかならない。"
msgstr "But even if that happens, humans will never be equal."

msgctxt "15141"
msgid ""
"才能がある者とない者……\n"
"身分という壁はなくなっても、\n"
"今度は別の壁が立ちはだかる。"
msgstr ""
"Those who are talented and those who are not ... Even if the wall of status "
"disappears, another wall will stand up this time."

msgctxt "15226"
msgid ""
"だから俺は、どうにかして、\n"
"どんなに学がない人間でも、\n"
"どんなに剣が振れない人間でも、"
msgstr ""
"So I somehow, no matter how illiterate I am, no matter how hard I can swing "
"my sword"

msgctxt "15313"
msgid ""
"せめて楽しく生きられる\n"
"世の中を作りたいと思ってる。"
msgstr "At least I want to create a world where I can live happily."

msgctxt "15366"
msgid "兄弟……"
msgstr "brothers……"

msgctxt "15375"
msgid ""
"お前も持っておいてくれ。\n"
"勤王党の一員として。"
msgstr "Please bring you too. As a member of the Qin Wang Party."

msgctxt "15423"
msgid ""
"俺たちが剣や銃を持たなくて良くなった時……\n"
"その時初めて、この国に真の平等が訪れる。"
msgstr ""
"When we don't have to have a sword or a gun ... Only then will true equality"
" come to this country."

msgctxt "15508"
msgid "それまで、俺と一緒に戦ってくれないか？"
msgstr "Until then, can you fight with me?"

msgctxt "15549"
msgid "土佐勤王党を俺と一緒に支えてくれ。頼む。"
msgstr "Please support the Tosa Qin Wang Party with me. ask."

msgctxt "15592"
msgid "ああ、分かった。"
msgstr "Oh, I understand."

msgctxt "15609"
msgid ""
"そうか！\n"
"よし、実はな、今晩高知城で東洋の親っさんと\n"
"今後の話をすることになってるんだ。"
msgstr ""
"Really! Well, actually, I'm going to talk to my oriental parents at Kochi "
"Castle tonight."

msgctxt "15698"
msgid "一緒に行かないか？"
msgstr "Would you like to go with me?"

msgctxt "15717"
msgid "そんなに大っぴらに会って大丈夫なのか？"
msgstr "Is it okay to meet so openly?"

msgctxt "15756"
msgid ""
"なぁに、高知城まで行けば、\n"
"親っさんの近臣が招き入れてくれる\n"
"手はずになってる。大丈夫だ。"
msgstr ""
"By the way, if you go to Kochi Castle, your parents' close vassals will "
"invite you. Should be fine."

msgctxt "15847"
msgid "そうか。"
msgstr "Really."

msgctxt "15856"
msgid ""
"それじゃお前は表で少し時間を潰しててくれ。\n"
"俺もすぐ支度していく。"
msgstr "Then you should kill a little time on the table. I will prepare soon."

msgctxt "18332"
msgid "武市"
msgstr "Takeshi"

msgctxt "18377"
msgid "龍馬"
msgstr "Ryoma"
